snippet.title: Sega Saturn - Tenchi Muyou! Rensa Hitsuyou (1997)
snippet.description:
DESCRIPTION
Tenchi Muyou! Rensa Hitsuyou is a Puzzle game, developed and published by Pioneer LDC, which was released in Japan in 1997.
